high_descs: however turn right and left move to the sidetable
Take the one pencil from kitchen rack
take the plate and move to wash room
After reaching the washroom, place the pencil above the toilet.
take one plate and knife to take and move to reach the bedroom
after reach the bedroom open to the drawer
then place the plate and knife on the drawer rack
anns.task_desc: Collect the plate and store it in the drawer in the bedroom.

high_descs: Turn left to reach the side table.
Pick up the pencil from the side table.
Turn around to head down the passage and turn left to reach the toilet.
Put the pencil on the plate on the toilet.
Pick up the plate from the toilet.
Turn around and head right to reach the drawer.
Put the plate in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with the pencil in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn back and reach the side table on the right side
Take a pencil from the table
Turn back and walk straight and turn left and again walk straight and enter into the bedroom and after reaching the end turn left to enter into the toilet and reach the plate in the toilet seat
Put the pencil in the plate
Take that plate along with pencil
Turn back and walk out of the toilet and turn right to reach the drawer
Open the drawer and put the plate along with pencil and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: put the plate along with pencil in the drawer
